*step-4.1.3 (08 Nov 2008)

  08 Nov 2008; Tomas Chvatal <scarabeus@gentoo.org> +step-4.1.3.ebuild:
  Version bump.

  13 Oct 2008; Jorge Manuel B. S. Vicetto <jmbsvicetto@gentoo.org>
  step-4.1.2.ebuild:
  Added a hard dep on qt-opengl as it was missing. Thanks to Peter Volkov
  for demonstrating the bug. Although step allows to enable or disable the
  use of the opengl functions at run-time, it forcefully tries to link to
  the qt-opengl library when building. Fixes bug 241182.

*step-4.1.2 (02 Oct 2008)

  02 Oct 2008; Jorge Manuel B. S. Vicetto <jmbsvicetto@gentoo.org>
  +metadata.xml, +step-4.1.2.ebuild:
  Add kde-4.1.2 into the tree from the kde-testing overlay.

